import axios from "axios"; import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import '../styles/weather.css' import LoginPage from './LoginPage' export default function Weather(){ var [coordinates,setCoordinates]=useState({}) var [weather,setWeather]=useState([]) var [main,setMain]=useState({}) var [visibility,setVisibility]=useState("") var [wind,setWind]=useState({}) var [clouds,setClouds]=useState({}) var [sys,setSys]=useState({}) var [name,setName]=useState("") useEffect(()=>{ axios.get("https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q=Kadapa&appid=55a0ebcb240d607f077934dec3f7822a") .then((res)=>{ setCoordinates(res.data.coord) setWeather(res.data.weather) setMain(res.data.main) setWind(res.data.wind) setClouds(res.data.clouds) setVisibility(res.data.visibility) setSys(res.data.sys) setName(res.data.name) }) }) var iconCode=weather.map((x)=>x.icon) var iconLink="http://openweathermap.org/img/w/" + iconCode + ".png" return( <>
{new Date().toDateString()}
{new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}
CURRENT WEATHER
{name},{sys.country}

Longitude: {coordinates.lon}

{weather.map((x)=> <>

Weather: {x.main}

Description: {x.description}

) }

Temp: {main.temp}

Feels like: {main.feels_like}

Max Temp: {main.temp_min}

Min Temp: {main.temp_max}

Pressure: {main.pressure}

Humidity: {main.humidity}

Sea pressure: {main.sea_level}

Ground pressure: {main.grnd_level}

Visibility: {visibility}

Wind: {wind.speed}

Clouds: {clouds.all}

); }
